data.description: Welcome HOME to this spacious traditional in Garretts Ridge, perfectly situated in the convenient Douglasville/Nebo/Acworth corridor.  Located across the street from the middle school, and 2 miles from the Ridge Rd. Kroger, this quiet 4 bedroom abode with a fire pit and a flat fenced in backyard is priced to sell coming in under $300k.  Boasting vaulted living space ceilings, master on main, and a 2 car garage with a workshop, this tasteful offering is the one you've been searching for!
